room_title: Escape room "Prison Break 2.0" by Escape Modesto in Modesto
room_description: You have been framed! You are locked in a maximum security prison awaiting execution for a crime you didn't commit. Many have attempted to escape this prison in the past and it has been rumored that those who may have escaped left behind secret messages and clues of their plans. You have one hour to escape before the prison guards return.
